quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Deε wͻn a wͻnni anidaasoͻ sε wͻne Yεn behyia no keka ne sε: “Adεn nti na yɛnsiane Soro abͻfoͻ ma yεn, anaa yɛnhunu yɛ Wura Nyankopͻn no? Ampa sε wͻn ara ama wͻn ho so, na wͻate atua ama no aboro so kεse."
  25,22,"Ɛda a wͻbɛhunu Soro abͻfoͻ no, saa da no εnyε asεmpa mma abͻneεfoͻ no. (Soro abͻfoͻ no) bεka sε: “Moma εhyeε kεseԑ nna (wͻn ne Soro Aheman mu foͻ no ntεm)“"
  25,23,"Yεbεba dwuma biara a (abͻneεfoͻ no) diiε no so, na Yεbεma no ayε sε mfuturo bi a atu ahweteε."
  25,24,"Ɛda no, Soro aheman no mu foͻ no benya asetena pa ne ahomegye bea pa."
  25,25,"Ɛda no a mununkum bεma ɔsoro mu adwidwa, na Soro abͻfoͻ besiane siane paa no,"
  25,26,"Saa Da no Ahennie paa no wͻ Ahummͻborͻ Hene no. Saa Da no, εbεyε den ama (Kaafirfoͻ) boniayεfoͻ no."
  25,27,"Saa Da no na (onipa) bͻnefoͻ no bεka ne nsa aka sε: “Mehunui a anka mekaa Ɔsomafoͻ no ho ne no faa kwan (pa) no so."
  25,28,"Ao, Adi ayε me, Mehunui a anka manfa asomasi yͻnkoͻ”."
  25,29,"“Ampa paa sε wama mayera afri Afutusεm no ho wͻ berε a yεde berεε me no. Ͻbonsam (yε obi a) odi onipa hwammͻ paa”."
  25,30,"Ɔsomafoͻ no nso bεka sε: ”Me Wura Nyankopͻn, nokorε sε, me nkorͻfoͻ no yii wͻn ani frii Qur’aan yi so”"
  25,31,"Saa ara na Yεmaa Nkͻmhyεni biara tamfo wͻ abͻneεfoͻ no mu. Nanso wo Wura Nyankopͻn som bo (ma wo) sε Ɔkwankyerεfoͻ ne Ͻboafoͻ."
  25,32,"Deε wͻn a wͻnnye nnie no ka ne sε: “Adεn nti na yensiane Qur’aan no mmͻ mu mma no prεko?” (Yesiane no saa) sεdeε εbεma w’akoma agyina pintinn, na Yεkenkan (Qur’aan no ma wo) nkakra nkakra, hyehyɛ no pɛpɛɛpɛ."
